HEADWORD: Jesuitical
<hw>Jes`u*it"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>j⟦eacute⟧suitique</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining to the Jesuits, or to their
